author: Frank Corder
title: Hosemann announces $7.8 million in tidelands returned to coast
text: GULFPORT -- Secretary of State Delbert Hosemann delivered $7.8 million to the Coast legislative delegation and the Department of Marine Resources on Tuesday. The money comes from tidelands leases, primarily to casinos, across the Coast's waterfront. Sunherald Posted October 14, 2015 - 5:37 am YallPolitics.Com now uses Facebook for comments.
